comment: "I can do everything: I act, I sing, I rap, I dance... Let's send the rest of these clowns home."
"I've worked with huge celebrities, like Rihanna, Ke$ha, and I'm the Queen Bee, so eat it up... and crown it. You're all fucking welcome."
"Me and Detox started drag together, and I'm just so excited to see her."
"I'm a pageant girl. Big hair, big makeup: from head to toe, it's a Roxxxy Andrews andrews project"
"honey, i'm serving up fish, tuna on a platter"
"jade is bubbly, she laughs a lot. I just like to be fabulous and have fun!"
"well, you both are going really home early, just so you know."
"this is the best quinceanera present ever!"
"automatically, Detox and Roxxxy Andrews were brrrrrrrrrrr... it's a little off-putting... rather, annoying"
"I'm known as the Vanessa Williams of drag, because after winning the title of Miss Gay America, the crown was taken away from me."
"you know I can clear the cackling from down the street"
"my name is jinkx Monsoon I'm 24 and I'm Seattle youngest MILF."
"I'm theatrically trained in the Broadway school of singing"
"I don't know about that Jinx yet, she's a little kooky."
Hello my name is Jason and I am 39 years old. I'm here because I was chosen by thousands of people in the online building contest
"You guys should be happy to know that everybody actually wanted me here!"
"I hope that me being voted on the show by a lot of people makes the other queens really intimidated"
"You're giving me pin-up, Kat Von Dee doll."
"Vivian is all about glamour. My beauty is everything."
"My name is Alaska and I'm 27 years old and I also have a very famous boyfriend whose name is Sharon Needles."
"this trashbag couture is definitely something else."
"Alaska definitely has big shoes to fill"
"my name is Honey Mahogany and I'm 28 years old"
"Honey Mahogany is like a RuPaul poster... but not quite as polished. sorry about it~! :)"
"I think I'm the first queen from San Francisco, actually."
"People get down on San Francisco for being a bunch of hippies, but there's so much beauty there. Have you seen Honey Mahogany?"
"My name is Ivy Winters. I'm 25 years old."
"Your top is awesome, it's so well tailored."
"I make costumes out of casette tape, paper cups, condoms. I will figure out a way to turn it into a costume."
"And I used to work as a clown for like eight years."
"I'm Monica Beverly Hillz, with a zee."
"I'm 27. Monica Beverly Hillz is very good at giving face."
"This might be the fishiest season ever, darlings."
"I have been called ghetto, banjy, trashy... I was raised in the ghetto, you know. I'm very street smart, and there's nothing wrong with that."
"I am Lineysha Sparx and I'm 24 years old."
"Lineysha is so fierce, so flawless, so sparkling."
"I'm very excited to be here, representing Puerto Rico.
"Lineysha's in the house, so watch out bitches!"
"I'm Coco Montrese and I'm 37 years old."
"and then walks in Coco Montrese. The face crack of the century."
"Alyssa, you want to tell the story or you want me to tell the story?"
"We haven't spoke in two years. The pageant tore our friendship apart."
"We were close. And I feel like I was bamboozled."
"Coco was the one back-stabbing me behind my back."
"Alyssa and I will have our moment later together, cuz we need a moment."
"I don't think she wants to talk about. But I want to talk about it. If she doesn't get sent home first."

"Welcome, my queens. I told you California was the place you oughta be, so you tightened up your tuck, and you flew to Beverly... Hills! Adjacent, that is. So whether you're a Fresh Princess of Bel-Air, a Malibu Barbie, or just serving Real Housewife realness, to get your big break in RuPauliwood, you need to make an even bigger splash and really shake things up."
"Oh, oh my goodness!~ An earthquake! My hair! Oooh~ I think it's the big one. Ooh, faster! faster! Ooh, slower, slower, slower, Ah! Cut!"
"Remember, to snatch this crowd, you need to fake it till you make it."
"Hello hello hello~! Welcome to RuPaul's Drag Race!"

"Now, I chose each of you because I see in you the raw "Charisma Uniqueness Nerve and Talent" that it takes to go all the way. In addition to winning the title of America's Next Drag Superstar, the champion of RuPaul's Drag Race will receive: a lifetime supply of Color Evolution Cosmetics, a one-of-a-kind trip courtesy of AlandChuck.Travel and headline Logos outrageous Drag Race Tour featuring Absolut Vodka cocktails perfected and some cash money, honey. Yes, child, to the tune of $100,000."
"Wow, I feel so excited, it's one hundred thousand of dollars. and I want to win that money."
"No more kidding around, girls. You're in the entertaint-ment capital of the world. And to make it in RuPauliwood, you've got to dive in the deep end. Are you ready for your closeup?"
"It's time for our first photoshoot. I am eager to see what the challenge is and i am super nervous."
"What do you think is going on right now?"
"Oh my gosh, talk about the elephant in the room, didn't see that.
"Now, say hello to the the amazing Mike Ruiz. Mike is here to shoot your Hollywood Splash Photo. What we're looking for is underwater, serving glamour."
"Today, we're doing an homage to old Hollywood, that's kind of a tribute to old Esther Williams films."
"Please note that there's no pee in the water."
"Try not to look like you're holding your breath."
"Jade would inhale a bunch of air and would hold it all in her cheeks like a chipmunk. That doesn't make for a very pretty glamour shot."
"I was giving Helen Keller drowning realness."
"On the Roxxxy Andrews with a splash."
"Detox fell off the wagon and into the pool."
"Serena ChaCha! The time has come for you to sink, for your life."
"Oh! Oh dear. I can see your seafood platter. Your paella is showing."
"Ok, there's a pole, hun. Hold onto the pole."
"Look it! It looks like frog legs."
"What the fuck was that about, guys?!"
"It's not your quinceanera anymore, is it?"
"I'm not tucked at all. So the dress was doing this [waves dress] the whole time."
"So you thought you were being cute today by being comfortable with your non-tuck, and ????? together..."
"I'm not a fan of girls who don't tuck. Look like a woman. It's female impersonation at the end of the day."
"Your legs look like calamari when you do that."
"Jinkx Monsoon, welcome to the drag lagoon!"
"I don't know how to swim. I learned how to swim by one of my uncles pushing me off a log, into a river."
"First time under the water, I lost both of my contacts. i was blinded within seconds."
"Okay, you look a little scared underwater."
"I think we're going to have to call it a wrap."
"Jinkx, there's got to be a morning after."
"Girl, you're gonna put Shelley Winters out of work!"
"Oh, Alaska's underwater. Damn you, global warming!"
"Okay. Yeah, you're head's not going very deep."
"And keep your hair out of your face!"
"I can't get deep enough. I don't know how to do it!"
"Alaska, she got really frustrated, and it showed."
"Alright, alright. I can't do it. I failed."
"We will offer you one more dip if you want to take it."
"I can't believe that. I'm in shock."
"I've completely blown it. I don't know what I'm gonna to do."
"Push your dress down when you get underwater."
"In the future, you should handwash your woolens."
"Lineysha's body language was so incredibly graceful and dancerly, it was amazing."
"Sorry to say, that satin will never be the same."
"Chicken of the sea! Serving Tuna Turner."
"Okay y'all. Somebody forgot to tell them that black people don't swim."
